    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The subjects see a murder of crows descend upon them and assault them. They suffer a -10 penalty to Spot and Listen checks, must make a Concentration check (DC 15) to use any action requiring concentration, and lose their Dexterity bonus to Defense against the first attack made against them. If attacked, the illusion immediately fades.<br><br>A creature cannot be affected by this technique more than once per hour.</p>\n\n\n\n",
